OL,3,CBritish Airways passengers suffer
OL,4,Cbaggage chaos at Heathrow
OL,6,FBritish Airways is unable to put a
OL,7,Ftimeframe on when passengers will be
OL,8,Freunited with bags after a 'technical
OL,9,Ffault' caused chaos at Heathrow.
OL,11,FPassengers flying out from London
OL,12,Farrived at destinations to discover
OL,13,Ftheir luggage was not on the plane.
OL,15,FOthers waited hours at the carousel in
OL,16,FTerminal Five before realising their
OL,17,Fbags were not coming.
OL,19,FBA declined to say how many flights,
OL,20,Fpassengers or bags weee affected.
