OL,3,CBritish Airways passengers suffer
OL,4,Cbaggage chaos at Heathrow
OL,6,FA spokesperson said passengers were
OL,7,Fasked to fill out a form, leaving a
OL,8,Fforwarding address so bags could be
OL,9,Fdelivered by courier.
OL,11,FExtra staff have been called in to
OL,12,Fspeed up efforts to deal with the
OL,13,Fbacklog.
OL,15,FA British Airways spokesman said:
OL,16,F"We've apologised to those customers
OL,17,Fwho were unable to travel with their
OL,18,Fluggage due to a temporary technical
OL,19,Ffault that was outside of our control.
